  "redesignRationale": "The original site content is rich with technical and clinical authority but often presented in standard web formats. The redesign leverages a 'Dark Mode' specifically chosen to resonate with the 'night shift' reality of ICU work and the 'dark mode' preference of developers. By organizing the projects into a high-density Bento grid, we treat his portfolio pieces as 'modules' in a system, reinforcing his systems-engineering mindset. The typography is kept strictly utilitarian (Inter) to reflect the serious nature of healthcare data.",
  "prototypeHtml": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\" class=\"scroll-smooth\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>David Everly | Nurse Practitioner & AI Engineer</title>\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com\"></script>\n    <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <script>\n        tailwind.config = {\n            darkMode: 'class',\n            theme: {\n                extend: {\n                    fontFamily: {\n                        sans: ['Inter', 'sans-serif'],\n                    },\n                    colors: {\n                        slate: {\n                            850: '#152033', // Custom deep background\n                            900: '#0F172A',\n                        },\n                        teal: {\n                            500: '#14B8A6',\n                            600: '#0D9488',\n                        }\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n        }\n    </script>\n    <style>\n        /* Custom Scrollbar */\n        ::-webkit-scrollbar {\n            width: 8px;\n        }\n        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {\n            background: #0F172A;\n        }\n        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {\n            background: #1E293B;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n        }\n        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {\n            background: #334155;\n        }\n        .glass-panel {\n            background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.7);\n            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);\n            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"bg-slate-900 text-slate-50 font-sans antialiased selection:bg-teal-500 selection:text-white\">\n\n    <!-- Navigation -->\n    <nav class=\"fixed w-full z-50 top-0 left-0 border-b border-white/5 glass-panel\">\n        <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 h-16 flex items-center justify-between\">\n            <div class=\"font-bold text-xl tracking-tight flex items-center gap-2\">\n                <span class=\"w-3 h-3 bg-teal-500 rounded-full animate-pulse\"></span>\n                David Everly\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"hidden md:flex gap-8 text-sm font-medium text-slate-400\">\n                <a href=\"#bio\" class=\"hover:text-teal-400 transition-colors\">About</a>\n                <a href=\"#projects\" class=\"hover:text-teal-400 transition-colors\">Engineering</a>\n                <a href=\"#clinical\" class=\"hover:text-teal-400 transition-colors\">Clinical</a>\n                <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"hover:text-teal-400 transition-colors\">Contact</a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <!-- Hero Section -->\n    <section class=\"relative min-h-screen flex items-center pt-20\">\n        <div class=\"absolute inset-0 z-0 overflow-hidden\">\n            <!-- Abstract Background: ECG meets Neural Net -->\n            <div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/2 h-full bg-gradient-to-l from-teal-900/10 to-transparent\"></div>\n            <svg class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-64 opacity-5\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 1440 320\">\n                <path fill=\"#fff\" fill-opacity=\"1\" d=\"M0,224L48,213.3C96,203,192,181,288,181.3C384,181,480,203,576,224C672,245,768,267,864,250.7C960,235,1056,181,1152,165.3C1248,149,1344,171,1392,181.3L1440,192V320H1392C1344,320,1248,320,1152,320C1056,320,960,320,864,320C768,320,672,320,576,320C480,320,384,320,288,320C192,320,96,320,48,320H0Z\"></path>\n            </svg>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center\">\n            <div class=\"space-y-8\">\n                <div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-teal-500/10 border border-teal-500/20 text-teal-400 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                    <span>M.S. AI Candidate</span>\n                    <span class=\"w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-500\"></span>\n                    <span>Nurse Practitioner</span>\n                </div>\n                <h1 class=\"text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight\">\n                    Bridging <span class=\"text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-400 to-teal-200\">Bedside</span> \n                    <br>and <span class=\"text-white\">Binary.</span>\n                </h1>\n                <p class=\"text-xl text-slate-400 max-w-lg leading-relaxed\">\n                    I combine over a decade of critical care experience with advanced machine learning engineering to build safer, smarter healthcare systems.\n                </p>\n                <div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-4\">\n                    <a href=\"#projects\" class=\"px-6 py-3 bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-500 text-white font-medium rounded-lg transition-all shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(13,148,136,0.3)]\">\n                        View Engineering Projects\n                    </a>\n                    <a href=\"#bio\" class=\"px-6 py-3 bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 border border-white/10 text-white font-medium rounded-lg transition-all\">\n                        Clinical Background\n                    </a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <!-- Hero Visual: Glass Card Stats -->\n            <div class=\"relative\">\n                <div class=\"glass-panel rounded-2xl p-8 transform rotate-2 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-500\">\n                    <div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-6\">\n                        <div>\n                            <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white\">System Status</h3>\n                            <p class=\"text-slate-400 text-sm\">Operational</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 animate-pulse\"></div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"space-y-4 font-mono text-sm\">\n                        <div class=\"flex justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-2\">\n                            <span class=\"text-slate-500\">Role</span>\n                            <span class=\"text-teal-400\">NP / ML Engineer</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"flex justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-2\">\n                            <span class=\"text-slate-500\">Education</span>\n                            <span class=\"text-slate-300\">Drexel M.S. AI '26</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"flex justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-2\">\n                            <span class=\"text-slate-500\">Focus</span>\n                            <span class=\"text-slate-300\">Deep Learning & Workflow</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"flex justify-between\">\n                            <span class=\"text-slate-500\">Stack</span>\n                            <span class=\"text-slate-300\">Python, PyTorch, Epic</span>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- Projects Grid (Bento) -->\n    <section id=\"projects\" class=\"py-24 bg-slate-850\">\n        <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6\">\n            <div class=\"mb-16\">\n                <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-4\">Engineering Portfolio</h2>\n                <p class=\"text-slate-400 max-w-2xl\">Independent development using public datasets and tools. Merging technical rigor with clinical utility.</p>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 auto-rows-[minmax(250px,auto)]\">\n                \n                <!-- Project 1: Large Feature -->\n                <div class=\"lg:col-span-2 glass-panel rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-teal-500/30 transition-colors group\">\n                    <div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-6\">\n                        <span class=\"text-teal-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase border border-teal-500/30 px-2 py-1 rounded\">Deep Learning</span>\n                        <svg class=\"w-6 h-6 text-slate-500 group-hover:text-white transition-colors\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\"></path></svg>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-3\">CNN Cardiac Rhythm Classification</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-slate-400 mb-6\">ECG rhythm classification on the public MIT-BIH dataset using a deep residual Convolutional Neural Network. Achieves high accuracy in distinguishing arrhythmias from normal sinus rhythm.</p>\n                    <div class=\"flex gap-2\">\n                        <span class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 bg-slate-900 px-2 py-1 rounded\">Python</span>\n                        <span class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 bg-slate-900 px-2 py-1 rounded\">PyTorch</span>\n                        <span class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 bg-slate-900 px-2 py-1 rounded\">MIT-BIH Data</span>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Project 2 -->\n                <div class=\"glass-panel rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-teal-500/30 transition-colors group\">\n                    <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-3\">Schedule Templater</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-slate-400 text-sm mb-6\">Generates schedule templates using Greedy Search with Simulated Annealing and Local Search/Repair algorithms to optimize coverage.</p>\n                    <span class=\"text-teal-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase\">Optimization</span>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Project 3 -->\n                <div class=\"glass-panel rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-teal-500/30 transition-colors group\">\n                    <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-3\">Cardiac Ischemia Prediction</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-slate-400 text-sm mb-6\">Comparative evaluation of shallow, deep, and residual‑enhanced multilayer perceptrons for classifying single‑lead ECG tracings.</p>\n                    <span class=\"text-teal-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase\">MLP / Diagnostics</span>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Project 4 -->\n                <div class=\"glass-panel rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-teal-500/30 transition-colors group\">\n                    <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-3\">QUIC Game Protocol</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-slate-400 text-sm mb-6\">A custom application layer protocol demonstration sending messages between terminals using the QUIC protocol.</p>\n                    <span class=\"text-teal-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase\">Networking</span>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Project 5: Achievement -->\n                <div class=\"glass-panel rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-teal-500/30 transition-colors group bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-900/20 to-transparent border-teal-500/20\">\n                    <div class=\"mb-4\">\n                        <span class=\"text-white font-bold text-sm bg-teal-600 px-2 py-1 rounded\">Systemwide Adopted</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-3\">ICU Transfer Note Standardization</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-slate-400 text-sm mb-4\">Designed a standardized transfer note improving communication between ICU and Hospitalist teams.</p>\n                    <p class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 italic\">\"Supports our patient safety goals...\" — Peter Jablin, MD</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- Bio / Clinical Section -->\n    <section id=\"bio\" class=\"py-24\">\n        <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center\">\n            <div>\n                <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">The Clinical Foundation</h2>\n                <div class=\"space-y-6 text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">\n                    <p>\n                        Since 2017, I have practiced as an <span class=\"text-teal-400 font-medium\">Acute Care Nurse Practitioner</span> in Emergency Medicine, Pulmonology/Critical Care Medicine, and Thoracic Surgery. My journey began in 2011, evolving from Unit Clerk to Registered Nurse to NP.\n                    </p>\n                    <p>\n                        As an ICU NP during the COVID pandemic, I witnessed how antiquated system processes hindered patient care and burdened stressed providers. Determined to find a better way, I returned to computer science.\n                    </p>\n                    <p>\n                        Today, I blend frontline clinical insight with a technical toolkit (Drexel M.S. AI candidate) to design intelligent systems. My calm demeanor and clinical insight—qualities that benefit patients—now drive my code.\n                    </p>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"mt-8 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n                    <div class=\"p-4 border border-white/10 rounded-lg\">\n                        <div class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1\">10+</div>\n                        <div class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide\">Years Clinical Exp</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"p-4 border border-white/10 rounded-lg\">\n                        <div class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1\">MS '26</div>\n                        <div class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide\">AI & Machine Learning</div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <!-- Timeline Visual -->\n            <div class=\"relative pl-8 border-l border-white/10 space-y-12\">\n                <div class=\"relative\">\n                    <span class=\"absolute -left-[37px] top-1 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-teal-500 ring-4 ring-slate-900\"></span>\n                    <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-white\">Nurse Practitioner</h4>\n                    <p class=\"text-slate-500 text-sm\">Critical Care & Thoracic Surgery</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"relative\">\n                    <span class=\"absolute -left-[37px] top-1 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-slate-700 ring-4 ring-slate-900\"></span>\n                    <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-white\">Epic Physician Builder</h4>\n                    <p class=\"text-slate-500 text-sm\">Certified Optimization Expert</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"relative\">\n                    <span class=\"absolute -left-[37px] top-1 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-slate-700 ring-4 ring-slate-900\"></span>\n                    <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-white\">Cybersecurity (ISC)²</h4>\n                    <p class=\"text-slate-500 text-sm\">Certified in Cybersecurity (CC)</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"relative\">\n                    <span class=\"absolute -left-[37px] top-1 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-slate-700 ring-4 ring-slate-900\"></span>\n                    <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-white\">M.S. Artificial Intelligence</h4>\n                    <p class=\"text-slate-500 text-sm\">Drexel University (Current)</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- Footer -->\n    <footer id=\"contact\" class=\"py-12 border-t border-white/5 bg-slate-950\">\n        <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 text-center\">\n            <h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-8\">Ready to optimize healthcare?</h2>\n            <div class=\"flex justify-center gap-6 mb-8\">\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors\">LinkedIn</a>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors\">GitHub</a>\n                <a href=\"mailto:contact@dmeverly.com\" class=\"text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors\">Email</a>\n            </div>\n            <p class=\"text-slate-600 text-sm\">© 2025 David Everly. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <!-- Chatbot UI Component -->\n    <div class=\"fixed bottom-6 right-6 z-50 flex flex-col items-end\">\n        <!-- Chat Window (Hidden by default, shown for prototype) -->\n        <div class=\"mb-4 w-80 bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden flex flex-col\">\n            <div class=\"bg-teal-600 p-4 flex items-center justify-between\">\n                <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n                    <div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-white/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center\">\n                        <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-white\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z\"></path></svg>\n                    </div>\n                    <span class=\"font-semibold text-white\">Triage Bot</span>\n                </div>\n                <button class=\"text-white/70 hover:text-white\">\n                    <svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"></path></svg>\n                </button>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"p-4 h-64 overflow-y-auto bg-slate-900 space-y-4\">\n                <div class=\"flex gap-3\">\n                    <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-900/50 flex items-center justify-center border border-teal-500/30\">\n                        <span class=\"text-xs text-teal-400\">AI</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"bg-slate-800 p-3 rounded-lg rounded-tl-none text-sm text-slate-300 border border-slate-700\">\n                        Hello. I'm David's AI Triage Assistant. Whether you're interested in my clinical background or my machine learning projects, I can help route you to the right information.\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex justify-end\">\n                    <div class=\"bg-teal-600 p-3 rounded-lg rounded-tr-none text-sm text-white\">\n                        Tell me about the cardiac projects.\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"p-3 bg-slate-800 border-t border-slate-700\">\n                <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Type a message...\" class=\"w-full bg-slate-900 border border-slate-700 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-teal-500\">\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- Toggle Button -->\n        <button class=\"w-14 h-14 bg-teal-500 hover:bg-teal-400 text-white rounded-full shadow-lg flex items-center justify-center transition-all hover:scale-105\">\n            <svg class=\"w-7 h-7\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z\"></path></svg>\n        </button>\n    </div>\n\n</body>\n</html>"
}